  "detailed_description": "Set in the year 2037, in a post apocalyptic world, 11 years after humanity has fallen and left forgotten.<br />\r\nDiscover what really happened, what happened to everyone and where did the machine come from.<br />\r\nYou the player take on the role of one of the last humans left on Earth, the Universe for all you know.<br />\r\nThe path in front of you seems clear,<br />\r\nEvade or fight your way through mechanical enemies, make a friend or keep to yourself,<br />\r\nbetray or be betrayed. Help, plunder, steal or murder.<br />\r\nLoose your humanity or remember who you where but above all do what you need to survive.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd remember, not everyone is your enemy but not everyone is your ally.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShape your world and become.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWho will you be..?",
